Description:
This occurs if my model (router_ip.xml) is simulated more than once. When the analysis view is open, the SSA-Hierarchical simulator can finish the simulation and generate results. If I click on the simulate button again, before the simulation completes, this exception occurs. To avoid this exception, I will have to close the analysis view and reopen it if I want to do the simulation again, as the first-time simulation does not generate this issue. The SSA-Direct has the same issue, and generates the same exception.

